26#pragma once
27
28#include <wtf/FileSystem.h>
29#include <wtf/FunctionDispatcher.h>
30#include <wtf/SHA1.h>
31#include <wtf/ThreadSafeRefCounted.h>
32#include <wtf/text/WTFString.h>
33
34#if PLATFORM(COCOA)
35#include <wtf/OSObjectPtr.h>
36#endif
37
38#if USE(GLIB)
39#include <wtf/glib/GRefPtr.h>
40#endif
41
42#if USE(CURL)
43#include <wtf/Box.h>
44#include <wtf/Variant.h>
45#endif
46
47namespace WebKit {
48
49class SharedMemory;
50
51namespace NetworkCache {
52
53class Data {
54public:
55 Data() { }
56 Data(const uint8_t*, size_t);
57
58 ~Data() { }
59
60 static Data empty();
61 static Data adoptMap(FileSystem::MappedFileData&&, FileSystem::PlatformFileHandle);
62
63#if PLATFORM(COCOA)
64 enum class Backing { Buffer, Map };
65 Data(OSObjectPtr<dispatch_data_t>&&, Backing = Backing::Buffer);
66#endif
67#if USE(GLIB)
68 Data(GRefPtr<GBytes>&&, FileSystem::PlatformFileHandle fd = FileSystem::invalidPlatformFileHandle);
69#elif USE(CURL)
70 Data(Variant<Vector<uint8_t>, FileSystem::MappedFileData>&&);
71#endif
72 bool isNull() const;
73 bool isEmpty() const { return !m_size; }
74
75 const uint8_t* data() const;
76 size_t size() const { return m_size; }
77 bool isMap() const { return m_isMap; }
78 RefPtr<SharedMemory> tryCreateSharedMemory() const;
79
80 Data subrange(size_t offset, size_t) const;
81
82 bool apply(const Function<bool (const uint8_t*, size_t)>&) const;
83
84 Data mapToFile(const String& path) const;
85
86#if PLATFORM(COCOA)
87 dispatch_data_t dispatchData() const { return m_dispatchData.get(); }
88#endif
89
90#if USE(GLIB)
91 GBytes* bytes() const { return m_buffer.get(); }
92#endif
93private:
94#if PLATFORM(COCOA)
95 mutable OSObjectPtr<dispatch_data_t> m_dispatchData;
96#endif
97#if USE(GLIB)
98 mutable GRefPtr<GBytes> m_buffer;
99 FileSystem::PlatformFileHandle m_fileDescriptor { FileSystem::invalidPlatformFileHandle };
100#endif
101#if USE(CURL)
102 Box<Variant<Vector<uint8_t>, FileSystem::MappedFileData>> m_buffer;
103#endif
104 mutable const uint8_t* m_data { nullptr };
105 size_t m_size { 0 };
106 bool m_isMap { false };
107};
108
109Data concatenate(const Data&, const Data&);
110bool bytesEqual(const Data&, const Data&);
111Data adoptAndMapFile(FileSystem::PlatformFileHandle, size_t offset, size_t);
112Data mapFile(const char* path);
113Data mapFile(const String& path);
114
115using Salt = FileSystem::Salt;
116SHA1::Digest computeSHA1(const Data&, const Salt&);
117
118}
119
120}
